public class LiaisonTestClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, LiaisonTrigger

Tests the establishment of contact and the management of interactions between an application and a liaison administration GUI through a JavaSpace. This functions as a standalone version of a LiaisonManager.
